      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: He turned west, but I heard wolves there too, so if he's still alive,
          I'd be surprised.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422256199180484815
      type: {class: OptionItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Okay, thank you for the information.
    - rid: 5422256199180484816
      type: {class: OptionItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Haven't you checked where it is?
    - rid: 5422256199180484817
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Sir, where are we going to go at night when we have to be on guard
          here?
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422256199180484818
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: If anyone goes into the forest, they do so at their own risk.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422256199180484819
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Good luck!
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
